                "company_url": "https://www.bublup.com",
                "location": "Arlington, VA (or remote)",
                "title": "Senior Angular/Angular JS Developer",
                "description": "<h3>The Job</h3>\n<p>Bublup is hiring software engineers with experience in JavaScript — ideally Angular or AngularJS — to create state of the art interfaces for large-scale and highly interactive applications. Our projects are ground-breaking in terms of how users interact with data and each other. We are looking for people who love to write code, but also have a great imagination.</p>\n<h3>Skill Areas</h3>\n<p>We want talented people who have experience with various technologies for front-end development, and who adapt to whatever the right architecture, languages, and libraries are to build the best total system and deliver the best user experience.</p>\n<h3>Some Important Skills:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>5+ Years experience in a highly relevant position with demonstrable command of JavaScript.</li>\n<li>Experience building SPAs. Angular or AngularJS would be a big plus.</li>\n<li>Degree in Computer Science or a related technical field, with strong understanding of programming concepts.</li>\n<li>Solid understanding and experience of software development tools, including Package Managers, Continuous Integration, Build Tools, Task Runners, Unit Testing, Ticket/Bug Tracking.</li>\n<li>Experience with responsive design.</li>\n<li>Demonstrable advanced knowledge of CSS and CSS techniques including css vars, flex, grid, animations, etc.</li>\n<li>Familiarity with common CSS frameworks like Material, Bootstrap, etc.</li>\n<li>Bonus points for:</li>\n<li>Familiarity with common font icon libraries such as Material Icons, Font Awesome, etc.</li>\n<li>Familiarity with fonts and typography.</li>\n<li>A minor (or experience) in a design related field.</li>\n</ul>\n",
                "how_to_apply": "<p>Email your resume to: <a href=\"mailto:careers@bublup.com\">careers@bublup.com</a></p>\n",
                "company_logo": "https://jobs.github.com/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBc09PIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--fd5aad627c848524f52a88efef732465173f775d/bublup.jpg"
