                "title": "Software Engineer Team Leader (Java Integration Team)",
                "description": "<p>We are Ocado Technology. We are building the software which powers our next-generation robotic picking and storage solution. This solution is a core component of our Customer Fulfilment Centres (CFCs) which are offered as part of the Ocado Smart Platform (OSP). OSP is being marketed to retailers globally as a world-class platform for grocery eCommerce.</p>\n<p>The Perception Robotics department aims to automate physical processes that require sensing and judgment through the use of robotics and machine vision.</p>\n<p>As a Team Leader in our Robotic Systems Integration team, you will:</p>\n<p>Actively participate in the design and development of back-end integration solutions (mostly in Java) internal for the robotic pick stations and between larger CFC systems.</p>\n<p>Grow, develop and lead the Robotic Systems Integration team.</p>\n<p>Optimize the delivery process, the tooling and techniques to achieve fast and robust delivery.</p>\n<p>Effectively communicate with other teams and stakeholders across Ocado locations (Product teams, Research teams, UX, other R&amp;D teams etc.).</p>\n<p>You will be working actively within Ocado Sofia dev center leadership to build a great place to work (contributing to processes like recruitment, branding, induction etc.).</p>\n<p>Requirements for the position:</p>\n<p>Essential</p>\n<p>Organisational and interpersonal skills with a can-do mindset.</p>\n<p>Strong technical hands-on background in building enterprise-grade backend systems, preferably in Java.</p>\n<p>Architectural awareness for systems that are dynamically evolving and are built to last (micro-services, messaging, API design, DB solutions, networking, scalability, monitoring, logging).</p>\n<p>To “feel at home” optimising CI/CD processes and achieve a state of the art quality of service and the underlying codebase.</p>\n<p>Deep knowledge in software testing and related processes and tooling.</p>\n<p>Internal motivation to achieve our common vision as a team.</p>\n<p>Advantage</p>\n<p>Project Management Experience</p>\n<p>Robotics or automation experience</p>\n<p>What we offer:</p>\n<p>Flexible working hours &amp; home office opportunity</p>\n<p>Development Exchange Program</p>\n<p>A choice of equipment</p>\n<p>Compliment card</p>\n<p>Additional medical insurance and life insurance</p>\n<p>International collaboration with colleagues from our other sites</p>\n<p>There’s a lot going on at Ocado Technology! Come and find out more about us at one of our online Webinars.</p>\n",
